01:28:26,067 --> 01:28:27,398
that was the charge.
这才是真正的指控罪名

1400
01:28:27,468 --> 01:28:30,528
The checking business brought to you by the great Dippity-Do Doyle.
这单生意是老滑头Doyle让我接的

1401
01:28:30,605 --> 01:28:32,903
If I didn't do what he said, he would have killed you and your mother.
如果我不按他说的做，他早就把你和你老妈给杀了

1402
01:28:32,974 --> 01:28:34,066
Believe me, kiddo.
相信我，小子

1403
01:28:34,142 --> 01:28:35,439
I have trouble focusing,
我无法集中精神

1404
01:28:35,510 --> 01:28:36,670
I consider leaving quickly,
我有点想尽快离开

1405
01:28:36,744 --> 01:28:38,143
but I will myself to stay.
但最终我强迫自己留下来

1406
01:28:38,212 --> 01:28:41,909
My job was to enter the banks and open an account.
我要做的就是到银行开户

1407
01:28:42,650 --> 01:28:44,777
I was the only one able to finesse my way in.
我可是唯一一个能做得神不知鬼不觉的人

1408
01:28:44,852 --> 01:28:47,082
The secret? The secret?
秘诀就是

1409
01:28:47,889 --> 01:28:49,550
Always go to a female teller.
永远去女出纳员负责的柜台

1410
01:28:50,425 --> 01:28:53,622
A black? Forget about the fucking blacks. Low fucking morale.
黑人？别提操蛋的黑人了，那些人一点道德都没有

1411
01:28:53,695 --> 01:28:57,927
Go to them? I couldn't get on fucking first base with a black teller.
去他们的柜台？那我一定连第一步都达成不了

1412
01:28:57,999 --> 01:29:01,491
It's early in the month, so he hasn't gone through his disability check yet.
现在还是月初，这表示他才刚刚拿到政府补贴

1413
01:29:01,569 --> 01:29:03,002
This means he has been drinking.
他一定会去喝酒

1414
01:29:03,071 --> 01:29:05,938
...good Russian vodka. Not that rotgut crap.
...上好的黑伏特加，可不是那种掺水的垃圾

1415
01:29:07,942 --> 01:29:09,000
Want some?
来点？

1416
01:29:09,077 --> 01:29:10,066
Uh, no thanks.
呃，不了谢谢

1417
01:29:12,580 --> 01:29:13,569
New teeth?
补牙了？

1418
01:29:14,048 --> 01:29:15,072
Huh?
哈？

1419
01:29:15,149 --> 01:29:16,776
You got some new teeth. - Yep.
你去补牙了 - 是啊

1420
01:29:16,851 --> 01:29:20,048
Courtesy of Uncle Sam.Best dentist in the world.
那可真是世界上最好的牙医诊所

1421
01:29:21,522 --> 01:29:22,819
Looks nice.
看上去不错

1422
01:29:22,890 --> 01:29:25,120
Here, I brought you something.
给你，我给你带了点东西

1423
01:29:27,395 --> 01:29:29,386
What the hell is this?
这是什么东西？

1424
01:29:29,464 --> 01:29:30,556
It's a book of poems.
一本诗集

1425
01:29:30,631 --> 01:29:31,655
Poems.
诗

1426
01:29:32,166 --> 01:29:33,827
I wrote it.
我的作品

1427
01:29:33,901 --> 01:29:35,163
Actually, it's getting an award.
事实上，它有可能会获奖

1428
01:29:35,236 --> 01:29:36,669
An award, from whom?
奖？哪的奖？

1429
01:29:36,738 --> 01:29:38,706
From Pen. - Pen.
（注：PEN/Voelcker Award for Poetry，美国一诗作类文学奖）

1430
01:29:39,107 --> 01:29:41,132
Are they giving you a pen?
他们会奖励你一根笔么？

1431
01:29:45,580 --> 01:29:47,207
Is it dedicated to me?
这本书是献给我的么？

1432
01:29:47,915 --> 01:29:49,576
No. No?
不是 - 不是？

1433
01:29:49,650 --> 01:29:51,208
Am I in it?
里头提到我了么？

1434
01:29:51,285 --> 01:29:53,116
There are some poems that refer to you.
有几首诗是以你为参考的

1435
01:29:53,354 --> 01:29:55,288
Oh. Let's see.
哦，让我看看

1436
01:29:59,894 --> 01:30:04,831
"I'll bend each finger back Until the bottle falls
“我将攥紧每一根手指/直到酒瓶落下

1437
01:30:04,999 --> 01:30:07,433
"Until the bone snaps
“骨节折断

1438
01:30:07,502 --> 01:30:10,232
"Save him by destroying his hands"
“毁掉他的双手/予他救赎

1439
01:30:10,738 --> 01:30:13,138
Do I detect a touch of hostility?
我好像从文字里嗅到了敌意？

1440
01:30:13,207 --> 01:30:16,404
I'm doing a reading of it tonight at a book store.
我今晚在书店开朗读会

1441
01:30:17,578 --> 01:30:20,172
You can come,if you would like to.
如果你想来的话也可以

1442
01:30:25,019 --> 01:30:26,452
All right, all right.
好吧，好吧

1443
01:30:28,289 --> 01:30:30,052
I'm going to let you read it.
我现在给你看看这个

1444
01:30:30,124 --> 01:30:31,785
Your book? Yeah, The Button Man,
你的书？ - 对，《纽扣人》

1445
01:30:31,859 --> 01:30:35,158
also known as The Confessions of Christopher Cobb.
又作《克里斯托弗・柯布的自白书》

1446
01:30:36,197 --> 01:30:37,596
You mean it actually exists?
这东西还真的存在啊？

1447
01:30:37,732 --> 01:30:39,131
Of course it exists.
当然了

1448
01:30:40,101 --> 01:30:41,295
Where the fuck is it?
跑哪去了？

1449
01:30:41,369 --> 01:30:42,859
It's somewhere here.
就在这房间的某个地方

1450
01:30:42,937 --> 01:30:46,429
Give me a hand here, look in these boxes. Look for a blue folder.
搭把手，去那些箱子里找一个蓝色的文件夹

1451
01:30:59,420 --> 01:31:00,910
I think I may have it here.
我记得是在这儿

1452
01:31:00,988 --> 01:31:02,615
Yeah. This is it.
没错，这就是了

1453
01:31:08,095 --> 01:31:09,926
Here it is, part one.
给你，第一部分

1454
01:31:10,865 --> 01:31:13,356
This is part one? How many parts are there?
只是第一部分？总共有多少个？

1455
01:31:13,434 --> 01:31:15,561
12. Eight are in existence.
12个，我已经写了8个部分

1456
01:31:18,406 --> 01:31:20,772
"Clink, clank, clunk.I think that I am drunk."
“叮，铛，咚，我想我已经醉了。”

1457
01:31:20,842 --> 01:31:24,972
Don't read it here, for Christ's sake. That part's a musical.
哦天啊，这里别用念的，它应该被唱出来

1458
01:31:25,046 --> 01:31:27,913
I will read it right away and get it back to you.
我读完就还给你

1459
01:31:27,982 --> 01:31:29,244
Don't steal anything.
可别偷走什么啊

1460
01:31:30,051 --> 01:31:31,382
I promise.
保证不会

1461
01:31:33,020 --> 01:31:35,215
I read his book in one afternoon.
某天下午我把它读完了

1462
01:31:35,289 --> 01:31:36,847
It's a masterpiece.
真是一流的杰作

1463
01:31:37,658 --> 01:31:39,057
I read your poems.
我读了你的诗

1464
01:31:39,126 --> 01:31:40,593
That one about the gun is heavy.
关于枪的那首有点沉重

1465
01:31:40,661 --> 01:31:42,822
Of course it's an inherited quality.
当然啦，既然遗传了我的才能，品质自然有保证

1466
01:31:42,897 --> 01:31:44,922
If you didn't write well,I would be surprised.
如果你写得很差，那我才会吃惊呢

1467
01:31:44,999 --> 01:31:47,229
For 30 pages it shows promise.
前30面给人以相当高的期待值

1468
01:31:47,668 --> 01:31:49,932
Then like his life,it soon falls apart
紧接着，就像他的人生那样，行文的骨架彻底被打散了

1469
01:31:50,004 --> 01:31:52,234
and dissipates into incoherence.
他开始语无伦次

1470
01:31:53,241 --> 01:31:55,368
His manuscript is incomplete.
他的书稿是不完整的

1471
01:31:55,810 --> 01:31:57,334
As far as I can tell,
我只能说

1472
01:31:57,645 --> 01:31:59,476
the only completed book about my father
完成这唯一一本相对完备的关于我父亲的书的

1473
01:31:59,547 --> 01:32:02,015
would be the book that fell to me to write.
重任就此落在了我的肩上

1474
01:32:02,083 --> 01:32:07,487
Me, my father's un-credited, uncompliant ghost writer.
我，一名永无怨言，无名无分，隶属于我父亲的影子写手

1475
01:32:08,422 --> 01:32:09,912
I've been in touch with Little Brown.
我和小布朗取得了联系

1476
01:32:09,991 --> 01:32:12,482
They are doing my book. Four million dollars in advance.
他们正在编辑我的书，预付给我四百万美元

1477
01:32:13,928 --> 01:32:16,624
Little Brown said my book's a masterpiece.
小布朗说我的书是杰作

1478
01:32:16,697 --> 01:32:19,222
Everything I write is a masterpiece.
当然，我书写的一切皆为杰作

1479
01:32:22,303 --> 01:32:25,033
"The eyes of the action hero cut from the poster
“从海报上剪下的/英雄的双眼

1480
01:32:25,106 --> 01:32:27,666
"All that concrete pressing down
“重重的水泥压下

1481
01:32:27,742 --> 01:32:30,438
"A fine edge gleams around your body
“你的身体闪烁着清晰的边界

1482
01:32:31,879 --> 01:32:34,074
"As if it could be contained
“似要张开双臂将其容纳

1483
01:32:39,921 --> 01:32:44,415
"The way each finger is licked,dipped in and rubbed across the gums
“好似在牙龈上轻拭

1484
01:32:45,092 --> 01:32:46,821
"Until the teeth go away
“陪伴直至牙齿脱落的每根手指

1485
01:32:47,428 --> 01:32:48,725
"Even my hands kiss you
“我愿以手吻你

1486
01:32:50,164 --> 01:32:52,655
"A night broken down into grains
“让暗夜破碎成谷粒

1487
01:32:53,467 --> 01:32:55,867
"If you find yourself lost, dig
“如果你迷失方向，快

1488
01:32:56,571 --> 01:32:58,835
"A cave in the snow, quickly
“在雪中掘出存身的洞窟

1489
01:32:58,906 --> 01:33:01,431
"You need shelter against the night
“你需要庇护以对抗漫漫长夜

1490
01:33:01,842 --> 01:33:04,140
"A candle could keep you alive
“一支蜡烛可挽留你的生命

1491
01:33:04,211 --> 01:33:08,079
"The engine of your lungs will heat the air around you
“让你的肺叶运转/以加热四下的空气

1492
01:33:08,149 --> 01:33:10,208
"Someone will miss you
“某些思念你的人

1493
01:33:10,284 --> 01:33:12,275
"They will send out dogs
“将派出援救的犬

1494
01:33:13,521 --> 01:33:15,819
"You must be somewhere,right?"
“你一定就在某处，对吗？”

1495
01:33:22,163 --> 01:33:23,596
Thank you.
谢谢

1496
01:33:26,634 --> 01:33:28,101
There you go.
给你

1497
01:33:28,603 --> 01:33:30,628
Thanks.Thanks for coming.
谢谢，谢谢捧场

1498
01:33:37,678 --> 01:33:38,804
Hey. - Hey.
嘿 - 嘿

1499
01:33:39,380 --> 01:33:40,574
Uh, he's here.
呃，他来了

1500
01:33:42,817 --> 01:33:46,048
Jonathan, this is Inez.Inez, this is Jonathan.
乔纳桑，这是伊内兹。伊内兹，这是乔纳桑

1501
01:33:46,120 --> 01:33:47,985
A very great pleasure.
很高兴见到你

1502
01:33:48,522 --> 01:33:49,648
It's good to meet you.
我也是

1503
01:33:49,724 --> 01:33:52,591
And this is Maeve,your granddaughter.
这是玛芙，你的孙女

1504
01:33:55,296 --> 01:33:56,524
Would you like to hold her?
想要抱抱她么？

1505
01:33:56,664 --> 01:33:57,926
Uh, that's okay.
呃，算了吧

1506
01:33:58,132 --> 01:33:59,292
No, he can hold her.
没关系，他可以的

1507
01:33:59,533 --> 01:34:01,296
I have held babies before, Nicholas.
我又不是没抱过小孩，尼古拉斯

1508
01:34:08,175 --> 01:34:09,267
See?
看到没？

1509
01:34:12,013 --> 01:34:13,139
See?
看到了吧？

1510
01:34:17,284 --> 01:34:18,376
See?
看到没？

1511
01:34:20,521 --> 01:34:21,579
See?
看到没？

1512
01:34:23,991 --> 01:34:24,980
See?
看到没？

1513
01:34:25,926 --> 01:34:27,120
Yeah, I see.
是啊，我看到了

1514
01:34:33,968 --> 01:34:35,902
All right, Nicholas,you can have it.
好了，尼古拉斯，你可以留下我的手稿

1515
01:34:36,637 --> 01:34:38,434
I bequeath it to you.
我授予你继承的权力

1516
01:34:40,274 --> 01:34:42,174
You have the last word.
结尾就拜托你了

1517
